{"tid":1767510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得其實廣東示威單嘢好鬼？","createTime":"2019-12-03T11:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T11:33:39.000Z","uid":181310,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"078e084faf0c7ec73b7313282c1360de1956b6cf","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"大陸人出嚟示威就正常嘅 只係大陸啲消息封鎖咗我地平時唔知啫<br />\n但問題嚟啦<br />\n點解今次好似啲消息傳得出嚟咁快？<br />\n係咪大陸特登開綠燈？<br />\n<br />\n第二 有冇人覺得大陸政府4日就妥協好唔正常<br />\n仲要又肯釋放示威者咁好死<br />\n公安又肯出嚟同人傾<br />\n而另一邊廂嘅香港政府<br />\n半年都未應承晒啲訴求<br />\n黑警又日日發癲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">完全同大陸係反比</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟無知一想 <br />\n呢個會唔會係大陸政府洗白自己嘅方法？<br />\n然後就迫香港政府唔好應承啲訴求<br />\n將今次風波嘅所有責任推晒落香港政府到<br />\n自己就扮撚到好民主咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e806922005f2fbb5e110140e0bbcf8d545df05c8","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"求高人指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d95cdc2618ac9fb97ca984f9f0535ed014fd68","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"274033b3a90b638487f9df5e397d632767094072","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926a8fd4f9c0725ad831d661d4260faf47279c4d","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b46993a2eb7bb3d6ac57a5ce124e832d1bef7d8d","tid":1767510,"uid":214192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"佢咁快跪係驚內亂？<br />\n年中都唔少呢啲衝突，係冇傳出嚟咋嘛<br />\n但佢話特赦同比救援就真係有啲驚，雖則都知佢會秋後算賬<br />\n但佢呢一跪會唔會造成更大型嘅示威呢？"},{"pid":"f6f9530eac2bff656a064ded2f595456bbc76aa4","tid":1767510,"uid":181310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46993a2eb7b